about_me:
Hi!

I'm not asking you to enable error reporting, share the verbatim error message, inspect variables... to annoy you and show off how much fancy stuff I know. That's the straightforward problem solving method. Why guess and try random stuff for days when the language engine can tell you the exact issue? If you don't know what I mean or how to apply it, please don't pretend you didn't read my comments. Instead, ask for clarifications—I'll be glad to guide you.
